<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Other_signals">Other signals</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Racing_Rules_of_Sailing&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Other signals"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<table class="wikitable">

<tbody><tr style="text-align: center; font-weight: bold;">
<td colspan="2" width="120px">Flag signal</td>
<td width="100px">Number of sound signals when raised</td>
<td width="100px">Number of sound signals when lowered</td>
<td width="500px">Description
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td width="90px"><figure class="mw-halign-center mw-image-border" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:ICS_Lima.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/ICS_Lima.svg/50px-ICS_Lima.svg.png" decoding="async" width="50" height="50" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/ICS_Lima.svg/75px-ICS_Lima.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/ICS_Lima.svg/100px-ICS_Lima.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="600" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
</td>
<td width="30px" align="center"><b>L</b>
</td>
<td><figure class="mw-halign-center" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Speaker_Icon.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/20px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png" decoding="async" width="20" height="20" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/30px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/40px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="500" data-file-height="500" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
</td>
<td>
</td>
<td>When displayed afloat means: Come within hail or follow this boat.
<p>When displayed ashore means: A notice to competitors has been posted.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><figure class="mw-halign-center mw-image-border" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:ICS_Mike.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/ICS_Mike.svg/50px-ICS_Mike.svg.png" decoding="async" width="50" height="50" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/ICS_Mike.svg/75px-ICS_Mike.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/ICS_Mike.svg/100px-ICS_Mike.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="600" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
</td>
<td align="center"><b>M</b>
</td>
<td align="center"><figure class="mw-halign-center" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Speaker_Icon.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/20px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png" decoding="async" width="20" height="20" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/30px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/40px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="500" data-file-height="500" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure> <b>...</b> <figure class="mw-halign-center" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Speaker_Icon.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/20px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png" decoding="async" width="20" height="20" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/30px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/40px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="500" data-file-height="500" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
</td>
<td>
</td>
<td>Indicates a boat or an object displaying this signal replaces a missing mark.
<p>Repeated sound signals should be made to draw attention to the signal.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><figure class="mw-halign-center mw-image-border" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:ICS_Yankee.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/23/ICS_Yankee.svg/50px-ICS_Yankee.svg.png" decoding="async" width="50" height="50" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/23/ICS_Yankee.svg/75px-ICS_Yankee.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/23/ICS_Yankee.svg/100px-ICS_Yankee.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="600" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
</td>
<td align="center"><b>Y</b>
</td>
<td><figure class="mw-halign-center" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Speaker_Icon.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/20px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png" decoding="async" width="20" height="20" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/30px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/40px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="500" data-file-height="500" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
</td>
<td>
</td>
<td>All people on board should wear a personal life jacket or personal buoyancy.
<p>Indicates a protest if displayed by a competitor during <a href="/wiki/Match_racing" title="Match racing">match racing</a>.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><figure class="mw-halign-center mw-image-border" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Auto_Racing_Plain_Blue.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fe/Auto_Racing_Plain_Blue.svg/50px-Auto_Racing_Plain_Blue.svg.png" decoding="async" width="50" height="38" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fe/Auto_Racing_Plain_Blue.svg/75px-Auto_Racing_Plain_Blue.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fe/Auto_Racing_Plain_Blue.svg/100px-Auto_Racing_Plain_Blue.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="800" data-file-height="600" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
</td>
<td align="center"><b>BLUE</b>
</td>
<td>
</td>
<td>
</td>
<td>When displayed the race committee boat is in position at the finishing line.
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><figure class="mw-halign-center mw-image-border" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Red_flag.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/43/Red_flag.svg/50px-Red_flag.svg.png" decoding="async" width="50" height="33" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/43/Red_flag.svg/75px-Red_flag.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/43/Red_flag.svg/100px-Red_flag.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="400" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
</td>
<td align="center"><b>RED</b>
</td>
<td>
</td>
<td>
</td>
<td rowspan="2">Displayed by a competitor:
<p>Indicates a protest by this competitor in <a href="/wiki/Fleet_racing" title="Fleet racing">fleet racing</a>.<br />
Indicates a request for redress in match racing.
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><figure class="mw-halign-center mw-image-border" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:ICS_Bravo.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f7/ICS_Bravo.svg/50px-ICS_Bravo.svg.png" decoding="async" width="50" height="50" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f7/ICS_Bravo.svg/75px-ICS_Bravo.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f7/ICS_Bravo.svg/100px-ICS_Bravo.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="600" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
</td>
<td align="center"><b>B</b>
</td>
